item.title: Running Server
item.dc:creator: @abatssk8ter abatssk8ter
item.description:
@abatssk8ter wrote:

in the client Change Client.java/Loader.java’s Ips to match your no-ip’s ip.

also make sure the client doesnt have an anti leech.
